text:
I've been to SkinnyFats a few times and everything is always so amazing! 

I've had the following and hopefully I can post picks of it all:

Drunken monkey pancakes (these are a MUST HAVE);
Smoke in a bowl (this one okay just very bland);
Chix on Broadway sandwich (was really good);
Sweet Cheese Us' (Amazing!!!) and
Bleu Balsalmic (I'm not a tomato fan whatsoever but this was beyond delicious).
